song.title: Dancing Frogs
song.info:
This was my entry for the "Amiga Executable Music" compo at the Datastorm demo party in Gothenburg.
Somewhat rushed and handed in right around the deadline.
The audio track, recorded from a real Amiga, was graciously provided by Xiny6581.
Winner and only entry at Amiga Executable Music @ Datastorm 2013. Originally a Hively Tracker tune with a replayer added on top.
